node.text:
Registration is OPEN for the annual Alpha King Challenge 🍺 

We usually crown the winner for the best hoppy beer at @rockbottombrewery in Denver during the @greatamericanbeerfestival — but this year we’ll be live streaming the competition from our brewery on October 16 with @yakimachief. Hit the link in our bio to register for the epic battle of beers ⚔️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by 3 Floyds Brewing on July 16, 2021. May be a cartoon of text that says 'AVAILABLE NOW!!! 3 FLOYDS CHEER TEAM ALE'.

node.text:
Featuring art by @theartofskinner , our latest diabolical Double IPA is loaded with virtually every hop product known to man - producing pronounced bitterness and TONS of grapefruit, mango, and pineapple notes.  And the dank . . . Can’t forget about the dank 💨
 
The unrelenting force known as Cheer Team is available for a limited time in all 3 Floyds markets + at our kiosk. 💥

→ Find it near you at 3floyds.com

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by 3 Floyds Brewing on July 13, 2021. May be an image of drink and indoor.

node.text:
Cue Black Flag’s “Can’t Decide” . . . 

For those that want even more variety in their life, our kiosk is now offering six packs featuring two OG classics + our beer that was already in space LONG BEFORE any billionaires started messin’ around up there 🚀  Find your variety six pack of Alpha King, Robert The Bruce, and Space Station Middle Finger available starting today for a limited time only in our kiosk. ⚔️ 
For more info visit 3floyds.com

node.text: Holla at your boy this weekend for all your lake/beach/oceanfront/pond/river/stream/puddle shenanigans . . . 🤘

node.text:
This is no mirage, it's . . . FANTASMO. 🦖

You're sure to be the most popular cat at your next BBQ when you come equipped with a 64oz growler of our Mexican-style lager. 🍻 Perfect for summer sessions, Fantasmo is brewed true to the Bohemian tradition with a light body and mouthfeel and features a sparkly, bready aroma, with a subtly sweet taste and just a touch of bitterness. 
While you're at it, be sure to pick up a Fantasmo shirt when you're grabbing the beer - it's a welcome respite from the black Bolt Thrower shirts your friends have (finally!) been seeing you in. ⚡️
Fantasmo is only available in 64oz growlers for a limited time exclusively at our retail kiosk. For more info visit 3floyds.com

node.text:
Black tee event commencing now. ⚔️
Check out the new shirt drops in our kiosk and available online here. ⬇️
→ 3floyds.com for details

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by 3 Floyds Brewing on June 18, 2021.

node.text:
A BIZZARRE MONSTROSITY! 
AN ENIGMATIC CONUNDRUM! 
AN UNRELENTING FORCE! 

 CHEER TEAM HAS ARRIVED! 💥

Your eyes do not deceive you, as the unstoppable creation known as Cheer Team returns for even more carnage. ☄️ Brought to life with virtually every hop product known to man, (including real hops!), our latest Double IPA features an incredibly juicy and fruity hop profile, pronounced bitterness, and an uncompromisingly mouthwatering finish. 
Not to be outdone, we’ve also got some new Cheer Team gear to save you from its wrath . . . 🔥
Find the beer + gear hitting our retail kiosk today, and Cheer Team Ale will be rolling out to all 3 Floyds markets over the next few weeks.
→ 3floyds.com for details 👁

node.text: Hailing from the dark recesses of the galaxy, we give you . . . MINOSTARR 💫 A hopped up Saison-style ale fermented in our stone tanks, Minostarr uses two differing yeast strains to produce a complex, amber colored conundrum ✨ With a tropical, bubblegum-like aroma mixed with some slightly earthy notes, Minostarr further confounds you with a moderately sweet and bitter finish. Available in growlers starting today for a limited time, you'll find this exclusively for purchase at our kiosk. For more info, visit 3floyds.com 🍺

node.text:
Start your summer off . . . SOUR 👾
 
For the month of June, stop by the kiosk + ask our team about our sour variety four pack. 💥 Featuring Chevalier, Molten Mirrors, Secret Savages, and Pear Bear, these mix packs are available for a limited time only at our kiosk. 
→ find out more at 3floyds.com 🍻
